"{\"uid\": \"inews.co.uk-sport-olympics-team-gb-taekwondo-beast-paris-2024-3181572\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"IMPARTIAL NEWS + INTELLIGENT DEBATE  Account  Rebecca McGowan will be competing alongside her boyfriend and training with Jade Jones in the biggest summer of her career so far  By Paul Eddison| Rebecca McGowan has always dreamed of competing at the Olympics but to book her place atParis 2024, she had to take down an icon of British Taekwondo.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 122, \"end\": 132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.812925789466195e-19, \"text\": \"Jade Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\"}, {\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9999947512179875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Taekwondo_Control_Board\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Taekwondo_Control_Board\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Taekwondo_Control_Board\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old from Dumbarton clinched a quota spot forTeam GBlast year, but then had to wait nervously to find out whether she had done enough to take that spot, or whether three-time world champion and double Olympic bronze medallist Bianca Cook (nee Walkden) would be selected in her place.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999980559551, \"rank\": 1.9439024376849026e-09, \"text\": \"Dumbarton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dumbarton_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\", \"score\": 0.9999141980820394, \"rank\": 8.58092803571921e-05, \"text\": \"Bianca\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no question that McGowan deserved, ranking higher in the 67+kg category, having won a World Championship silver medal and a pair of European bronzes during this Olympic cycle.\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most recent of those European podiums came in Belgrade in May, with Cook representing the Isle of Man as she did everything she could to stake a claim for the sole Team GB spot.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\", \"score\": 0.99999999986494, \"rank\": 1.3504952012569738e-10, \"text\": \"Belgrade\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\"}, {\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.268867363520715e-14, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Belgrade, however, it was McGowan who finished among the medals, as Cook went out at the quarter-final stage.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\", \"score\": 0.99999999986494, \"rank\": 1.3504952012569738e-10, \"text\": \"Belgrade\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\"}, {\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether that tipped the balance in the final decision from GB Taekwondo remains a mystery, but having finally had her place in Paris confirmed, McGowan has now been able to turn her focus to her Olympic ambitions.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7664595317009698, \"rank\": 0.30470029955293093, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.501274508988104e-12, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}, {\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.7823585241138424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"It's really exciting.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's nice to be here amongst it all now.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's nice to have the final say, you are going, get ready.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have all been getting ready all year, but now it's fully tunnel vision on that, I am not thinking about anything else.\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not do that (think about what the other person is doing).\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I imagine you would end up going crazy if you do that.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So all I did was focus on me.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I focused on what I did in my events and as long as I was putting out the best results I could, that is all I could do.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thankfully, it's good enough.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have just been making sure I am in top shape for Paris.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1949, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.7823585241138424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been focusing on myself, focusing on being the best me that I can be.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am trying to become a bit of a beast.\\\"\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cook and McGowan know each other well, with the Scot having travelled toTokyothree years ago as a reserve.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2084, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Japan, Cook claimed a second successive bronze medal on the Olympic stage, and admitted that missing out on a final shot at bronze was a devastating blow, having called for a fight-off with McGowan to decide the place.\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8267417383855358, \"rank\": 0.19176189623124007, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2376, \"end\": 2383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told theBBC: \\\"It feels like a massive loss, like grieving, because I am just absolutely devastated.\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not expect to just be selected, I wanted to earn that place and I thought that after dominating for so many years and the history that I have achieved for the sport, I deserved a fight-off.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris was always going to be my last Olympics and I know in my heart I was capable of turning those shiny [bronze] medals into a nice gold one, so I am devastated because it feels like my journey has been cut short.\\\"\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2710, \"end\": 2715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.7823585241138424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement, GB Taekwondo explained the reasoning behind the lack of a fight-off.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2944, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7664595317009698, \"rank\": 0.30470029955293093, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2947, \"end\": 2956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.501274508988104e-12, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic Selection Panel felt confident that Rebecca McGowan was in a better position than Bianca Cook to contribute to winning the best set of medals for Team GB.\\\"\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3063, \"end\": 3078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9999947512179875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 3109, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\", \"score\": 0.9999141980820394, \"rank\": 8.58092803571921e-05, \"text\": \"Bianca\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bianca_Montgomery\"}, {\"begin\": 3173, \"end\": 3180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.268867363520715e-14, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For McGowan, that Tokyo experience has been one of her main drivers on this Olympic cycle.\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3188, \"end\": 3195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 3202, \"end\": 3207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9949698170644153, \"rank\": 0.0050554482979375094, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even with such fierce competition for the British spot, she was determined not to relive the same scenario.\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3317, \"end\": 3324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9750905150058534, \"rank\": 0.01477886182809031, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"Being able to get that experience (in Tokyo) gave me a fire in my belly that I have never had before.\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3433, \"end\": 3438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9949698170644153, \"rank\": 0.0050554482979375094, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd done almost the entire prep and not being able to do that final part, I wasn't going to do it again for this one, I was making sure I was going to be the one that was fighting there.\\\"\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McGowan is one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sport's National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing her to train full-time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support.\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3686, \"end\": 3693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 3733, \"end\": 3741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 3733, \"end\": 3741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, McGowan will compete alongside her boyfriend and two-time world champion Bradly Sinden, who won silver in Tokyo, as well as fellow Olympic newcomer and housemate Caden Cunningham.\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 4099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3913, \"end\": 3918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.7823585241138424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3920, \"end\": 3927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 4026, \"end\": 4031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9949698170644153, \"rank\": 0.0050554482979375094, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 4088, \"end\": 4098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9999354009275992, \"rank\": 6.425160858601735e-05, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is inevitably a lot of excitement with the trio making up three-quarters of the taekwondo contingent heading over to France, with double Olympic championJade Jonescompleting the quartet.\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4224, \"end\": 4230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6692423403954273, \"rank\": 0.4941841237939242, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McGowan said: \\\"It's a nice house, we are all there prepping together, training together.\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4295, \"end\": 4302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a good house to be in.\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all in the excited phase, all ready to be there and embrace it all.\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's quite a high-energy house.\\\"\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As with many taekwondo athletes, McGowan has suffered her fair share of injuries, including a pair of broken ribs just a fortnight before she claimed her World Championship silver medal.\", \"from\": 4521, \"to\": 4707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4554, \"end\": 4561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with the Olympics now just around the corner, McGowan is doing everything to ensure she arrives in France in the best possible shape.\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4759, \"end\": 4766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 4812, \"end\": 4818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6692423403954273, \"rank\": 0.4941841237939242, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I am feeling good, I am feeling the best I have felt for a long time.\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have already started our prep camp, we have got training partners over.\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 5005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are in the deep of it right now.\", \"from\": 5006, \"to\": 5041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are just continuing on with that, ironing everything out, making sure that everything is as good as it can be.\", \"from\": 5043, \"to\": 5157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to make sure we are even more beasts for Paris.\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5207, \"end\": 5212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.7823585241138424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are training a lot.\", \"from\": 5215, \"to\": 5238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me it has to be smart training.\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the injuries I have carried, I train a bit smarter, if I have only got so many sessions, I have got to make the most of everyone.\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not let any time slide.\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got to make the most of every session.\\\"\", \"from\": 5440, \"to\": 5486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McGowan will compete on the final Saturday of the Games, along with Cunningham, knowing that her entire Olympic dream rests entirely on a single day.\", \"from\": 5488, \"to\": 5637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5488, \"end\": 5495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 5556, \"end\": 5566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9999354009275992, \"rank\": 6.425160858601735e-05, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But rather than worry about what might happen if she is not at her best on the day, McGowan is going to seize an opportunity.\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5723, \"end\": 5730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She concluded: \\\"It's something that is inevitable, you will think about it.\", \"from\": 5766, \"to\": 5841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's four years' worth of work for one day.\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have tried to switch my thought process around it.\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 5942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully, it could be done in six minutes, so give everything you can in those six minutes.\", \"from\": 5943, \"to\": 6035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then you could walk away Olympic champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 6036, \"to\": 6083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"National Lottery players raise more than \\u00a330million a week for good causes including vital funding into sport - from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 6085, \"to\": 6222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6085, \"end\": 6101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999999941942406, \"rank\": 5.79756330463472e-09, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To find out more visit:www.lotterygoodcauses.org.uk#TNLAthletes  Impartial news + intelligent debate  All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 6223, \"to\": 6345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 Associated Newspapers Limited.\", \"from\": 6346, \"to\": 6383, \"entities\": []}]}"